{
  "texts": [
    "A transformer is used, for instance, whenever a person searches for something on search engine like Google, Bing, etc.",
    "GPT-4, BERT (Bidirectional Encoder Representations from Transformers), RoBERTa, XLNet, and Megatron-Turing NLG are all examples of transformers.",
    "To find how seemingly unrelated data points in a sequence impact and rely on one another, transformer models are used by leveraging a growing body of mathematical techniques collectively referred to as attention or self-attention.",
    "Transformers, first detailed in a Google study published in 2017 (Vaswani et al., 2017), are cutting-edge and highly effective GAI models.",
    "Nowadays, text and voice are being translated in real time by transformers, allowing a wider range of people, including those with hearing impairments, to participate in meetings and classes."
  ]
}